607
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:02,400
and how did we win?

608
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:05,330
The Battle of Pingling?

609
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:07,750
At first,

610
00:30:09,460 --> 00:30:11,790
