614
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,550
But later,

615
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:21,040
His Highness set up an ambush
inside the pass,

616
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,880
so as long as Feng Suige

617
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:25,550
