He was just lucky.

624
00:30:42,830 --> 00:30:43,590
Besides,

625
00:30:44,030 --> 00:30:44,840
you...

626
00:30:45,350 --> 00:30:46,570
At that time,

627
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:48,040
you had no idea

628
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:50,550
why His Highness would

629
