639
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:14,470
Say it.

640
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:16,480
What military report?

641
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:18,160
Tell her, Weiran.

642
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:19,500
I can't drink anymore.

643
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:22,680
