644
00:31:24,590 --> 00:31:25,510
What report?

645
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:26,960
I have no idea.

646
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,540
I'm going to sleep.

647
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:36,590
Feng Suige said

648
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:39,920
