654
00:31:57,830 --> 00:31:58,240
Yes.

655
00:31:58,720 --> 00:31:59,270
Yixiao.

656
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:02,580
Your Highness?

657
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:04,160
What are you doing here?

658
00:32:04,310 --> 00:32:05,270
I saw that Ning Fei and Weiran

659
