667
00:32:24,310 --> 00:32:25,440
Then we shouldn't delay.

668
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:27,040
Come with me to the inn today.

669
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:29,270
I'll ask someone to
escort you back first tomorrow,

670
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:31,070
