688
00:33:15,970 --> 00:33:16,620
Yixiao.

689
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,200
Ever since you fell off the cliff,

690
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,270
I've had people investigating

691
00:33:19,270 --> 00:33:20,050
