754
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:23,000
All right.

755
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,920
Let her make her own decision.

756
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:26,000
I hope you'll

757
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:27,760
