788
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,240
That's right.

789
00:37:39,590 --> 00:37:41,050
I'm the Princess of Susha.

790
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:42,320
No matter who His Highness

791
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:43,320
liked in the past,

792
00:37:44,030 --> 00:37:45,760
