between our two kingdoms,

819
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:47,230
and His Highness won't need to
go to battle anymore.

820
00:38:47,230 --> 00:38:48,400
I'll work with him to protect

821
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:50,200
