843
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:37,610
I don't like crowds.

844
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:39,890
Are you afraid?

845
00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:46,250
Afraid of what?

846
00:39:47,150 --> 00:39:49,280
Since Your Highness has kindly invited me,

847
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,540
